QuickFindPrompt: Type in part of the Document ID or Company name to find the document

QuickFindSQL: Select {top} Bin as BinID, case ltrim(rtrim(Bin)) when '' then '[DEFAULT]' else Bin end as Bin from WarehouseInv Where (Bin like '%{replace}%') {where}

Select {top} Stock.StockId, Stock.StockID as [Stock Code], [Description], WI.WarehouseID as [Warehouse], CC.CostCentre as [Cost Centre], Stock.[BranchID] as [Branch Code] from Stock  Left Join CostCentre CC on CC.CostCentreID = Stock.CostCentreID AND CC.BranchID = Stock.BranchID Left Join WarehouseInv WI on WI.StockID = Stock.StockID AND WI.BranchID = Stock.BranchID Where ((Stock.StockID Like '%{replace}%') OR (CC.CostCentre Like '%{replace}%') OR (Stock.[Description] Like '%{replace}%')) {where}
QuickFindPrompt: Type in part of the Stock Code, Description or Cost Centre to find a Stock Code

QuickFindSQL: Select {top} Stock.StockId, Stock.StockID as [Stock Code], [Description], WI.WarehouseID as [Warehouse], CC.CostCentre as [Cost Centre], Stock.[BranchID] as [Branch Code] from Stock  Left Join CostCentre CC on CC.CostCentreID = Stock.CostCentreID AND CC.BranchID = Stock.BranchID Left Join WarehouseInv WI on WI.StockID = Stock.StockID AND WI.BranchID = Stock.BranchID Where ((Stock.StockID Like '%{replace}%') OR (CC.CostCentre Like '%{replace}%') OR (Stock.[Description] Like '%{replace}%')) AND (Stock.ItemCatID='dep') {where}
QuickFindPrompt: Type in part of the Stock Code, Description or Cost Centre to find a Stock Code

QuickFindSQL: Select {top} Stock.StockID, Stock.StockID as [Stock Code], [Description], WI.WarehouseID as [Group Code], CC.CostCentre as [Cost Centre], Stock.[BranchID] as [Branch Code] from Stock  Left Join CostCentre CC on CC.CostCentreID = Stock.CostCentreID AND CC.BranchID = Stock.BranchID Left Join (Select Distinct WarehouseID, StockID, BranchID From WarehouseInv) WI on WI.StockID = Stock.StockID AND WI.BranchID = Stock.BranchID Where ((Stock.StockID Like '%{replace}%') OR (CC.CostCentre Like '%{replace}%') OR (Stock.[Description] Like '%{replace}%')) AND (Stock.ItemCatID='pri') {where}

QuickFindSQL: Select {top} WarehouseID, WarehouseID as [Group Code], [WarehouseName] as [Inventory Group], BranchID as [Branch Code], Case isnull(isdefault,0) when 0 then 'No' else 'Yes' end as [Default] From Warehouse Where (Warehouse.WarehouseID Like '%{replace}%') OR (Warehouse.WarehouseName Like '%{replace}%')
